use my objective from the beginning of the year was to win the gold medal,\\\" Alcaraz said in an interview withYouTube channel MoluscoTV.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.085278615427587e-23, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The truth\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult moment\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"my objective\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"withYouTube channel\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"MoluscoTV\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And that week I felt the need to do it.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end that feeling can be wrong - to feel the need to do something - so in that moment when I did not do it, obviously after a defeat, 10-15 minutes after an objective you have not been able to complete, it's difficult to put everything in perspective.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"feeling\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"a defeat\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"an objective\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in that moment I felt that I had let my country down, that I had let the Spanish people down, for not winning the gold medal that everyone was expecting.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spanish people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why I reacted like that, letting my feelings go, and obviously speaking to the cameras, expressing myself in that moment, and showing to my country and to the world how I felt, I think it was necessary.\\\"\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my feelings\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"the cameras\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz has already won four Grand Slam titles in his promising career - winning twice at the French Open andWimbledon.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.085278615427587e-23, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four Grand Slam titles\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Open andWimbledon\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard also spent 36 weeks as world No.1 after becoming the youngest player to achieve the feat at the age of 19 in September 2022.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551259166, \"rank\": 0.24999999999997063, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"36 weeks\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"world No.1\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest player\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"the feat\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, he faces a long road ahead to catch up the Big Three of tennis - Djokovic,Roger Federerand his idolRafael Nadal- who collected a combined 66 Grand Slam titles between them.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long road\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"the Big Three\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis - Djokovic\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"Roger Federerand\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"his idolRafael\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"a combined 66 Grand Slam titles\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"oh carlitosyour fans are SO proud of you!!\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"carlitosyour fans\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"!pic.twitter.com/zB2o3MzTxj Our community members are treated to spec